SELECT "p"."Id", "p"."CreatedAt", "p"."Description", "p"."Icon", "p"."Image", "p"."IsActive", "p"."IsDeleted", "p"."Name", "p"."ParentCategoryId", "p"."ProductId", "p"."Slug", "p"."SortOrder", "p"."UpdatedAt"
